<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 07</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.78fr 1.22fr;
      gap: 20mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 82mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Bottom Summary */
    .summary-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .summary-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Product Grid */
    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .product-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 61mm;
      padding: 6mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .product-card.primary {
      background: var(--green);
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .product-image {
      height: 24mm;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.09);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.14);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 7px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.66);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .product-card.primary .product-image {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }

    .product-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .product-index {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
    }

    .product-card.primary .product-index {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    .product-title {
      margin: 0 0 4mm;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      line-height: 1.22;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      font-weight: 760;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .product-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.4px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .product-card.primary .product-desc {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }

    .product-tag {
      margin-top: 5mm;
      padding-top: 3mm;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.18);
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.78);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 750;
    }

    .product-card.primary .product-tag {
      border-top-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Product Lineup</div>

          <h1>
            일상과 산업 현장에<br />
            필요한 위생지 제품을<br />
            폭넓게 공급합니다
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 가정용 생활 위생지부터 산업·상업 공간에서 사용하는
            대용량 위생지까지 다양한 제품군을 제조하고 공급합니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-box">
          <div class="summary-title">6 Lines</div>
          <div class="summary-text">
            두루마리 화장지, 미용티슈, 키친타올, 점보롤,
            페이퍼타올, 물티슈까지 생활과 현장을 아우르는 제품군을 갖추고 있습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="product-grid">

          <div class="product-card primary">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/roll-tissue.jpg" alt="두루마리 화장지"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">01</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">두루마리 화장지</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                펄프 함유량이 많고 단단하며 길어 알뜰하게 사용할 수 있는 다목적 화장지입니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Roll Tissue</div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/facial-tissue.jpg" alt="미용티슈"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">02</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">미용티슈</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                천연펄프를 사용하여 먼지가 적고 표면이 부드러워 촉감이 우수한 제품입니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Facial Tissue</div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/kitchen-towel.jpg" alt="키친타올"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">03</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">키친타올</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                양면 엠보싱으로 흡수력과 부드러운 감촉을 갖춘 위생적인 주방 제품입니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Kitchen Towel</div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/jumbo-roll.jpg" alt="점보롤"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">04</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">점보롤</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                대용량으로 감겨 있어 청소와 관리에 용이하며 위생적으로 보관할 수 있습니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Jumbo Roll</div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/paper-towel.jpg" alt="페이퍼타올"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">05</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">페이퍼타올</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                타올의 두께와 흡수력이 뛰어나며 위생 관리가 필요한 공간에 적합한 제품입니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Paper Towel</div>
          </div>

          <div class="product-card">
            <div>
              <div class="product-image">
                PRODUCT IMAGE
                <!-- <img src="assets/wet-tissue.jpg" alt="물티슈"> -->
              </div>

              <div class="product-index">06</div>
              <h3 class="product-title">물티슈</h3>
              <p class="product-desc">
                무향, 무취, 저자극을 지향하는 고급 물티슈로 위생적이고 안전한 사용감을 제공합니다.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="product-tag">Wet Tissue</div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">07</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
